attributes.action: Free movement- Australia, Canada, New Zealand, United Kingdom + more. QE2 Realms
attributes.additional_details: To ask the UK Government and Parliament to dicuss the above and negotiate with other Governments and Her Majesty Queen Elizabeth II, a free movement deal with the listed and relaxed (made easier) movement with all other commonweatlh countries.
attributes.background: To ask the UK Government and Parliament to discuss the possibility of free movement between Australia, Canada, New Zealand, United Kingdom. To ask the UK Government and Parliament to discuss the possibility of relaxing (make easier) movement with all other commonwealth countries.
